Output docs/screenshot-04-coverage.png

Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set FontSize 13
Set Framerate 15
Set Padding 16
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type `nvim --cmd "set rtp+=." samples/eval-demo.fsx`
Enter
Sleep 3s
Show

Escape
Type "gg"
Sleep 500ms
Alt+Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "}j"
Alt+Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "}j"
Alt+Enter
Sleep 3s
